    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master The Blade</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the Sword: a sentient blade on a quest to find your Maker and to uncover the meaning of your life. This narrative platformer combines unique swordplay with puzzle-based exploration, inviting you to reflect while fighting to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292760/extras/38bbabeba4f294b238d4d1151468821d.poster.avif?t=1771878782\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292760/extras/38bbabeba4f294b238d4d1151468821d.webm?t=1771878782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292760/extras/38bbabeba4f294b238d4d1151468821d.mp4?t=1771878782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A World of Mystery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter the depths of an insane castle filled with puzzles, secret passageways, and unique mechanics. Nostalgic soul of classic platformers meets modern design that challenges your curiosity and imagination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292760/extras/edaf90860375800aa82ac929ae9d0e26.poster.avif?t=1771878782\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292760/extras/edaf90860375800aa82ac929ae9d0e26.webm?t=1771878782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292760/extras/edaf90860375800aa82ac929ae9d0e26.mp4?t=1771878782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defy Your Limits</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the world of The Lone Sword and carve through the mystery. Talk to fellow machines and slice through your enemies. Unbound by gravity, what will bring you down?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292760/extras/cdc4eaef9955ce8c343574fe28b76073.poster.avif?t=1771878782\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292760/extras/cdc4eaef9955ce8c343574fe28b76073.webm?t=1771878782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292760/extras/cdc4eaef9955ce8c343574fe28b76073.mp4?t=1771878782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Gameplay Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Sword is the Hero: Experience gameplay where the Sword is not just a weapon but the heart of the story—each swing and movement reflects your mastery and purpose.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzle-Based Exploration: Traverse a  castle, solving puzzles and uncovering secrets as you progress through a narrative-rich world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your entire body is dangerous: Slice through enemies, pick their weak spots, and don't let them hit back!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evocative Minimalism:  art direction defined by bold shapes and striking colors, free from visual noise.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Mechanical Fable: Immerse yourself in a whimsical and weird tale that explores themes of identity, creation, and purpose.</p></li></ul>",
